AttributeList.Text: ================================================================================ This module is used everywhere one alarm shall be generated when one (security) input becomes True. The alarm have a delay time set in millieseconds. The alarm can be True only when the input Enable Alarm is also True. The alarm can be True only when the input Disable Alarm is False. When the alarm is disable from HMI, a boolean output is available to inform the upper level and do action in the Alarm summary. When the conditions to generate the alarm is disappear, a boolean output is available to inform the upper level that the alarm can be reset. The alarm is reset by means of the AlarmResetPB signal. ================================================================================
